Subject: [PATCH 213/221] powerpc: add io{read,write}64 accessors
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: d54fc90cc9723d73eef25d09efcef412a6c89d60
